query:
SELECT 
  cl.id,
  cl.customerId,
  cl.apiId,
  cl.activationId,
  cl.timestamp,
  sa.name as apiName,
  sa.cancelLimit,
  sa.cancelWindowMinutes,
  sa.blockDurationMinutes
FROM cancellation_logs cl
JOIN sms_apis sa ON cl.apiId = sa.id
WHERE cl.customerId = 180002
ORDER BY cl.timestamp DESC
LIMIT 20;
